title: A10 Loadbalancer: Fans
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/a10
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the fans of A10 Networks ADC loadbalancers via SNMP
 (A10-AX-MIB, axFan table). It reports the fan status and the current
 speed in RPM.

 The service is always {OK}; the textual status and speed are shown in the
 service summary.

discovery:
 One service is created for each fan reported by the device.

item:
 The fan name as reported by the device, with a leading "Fan " prefix
 stripped.
